query: What is the net income per FTE in 2024 at Apple?
output:
In 2024, Apple's net income per full-time equivalent (FTE) employee was approximately **$571,561**.

This is calculated using:
*   Net income: $93,736 million (Consolidated Statements of Operations, September 28, 2024)
*   Full-time equivalent employees: 164,000 (Item 1. Business - Human Capital, as of September 28, 2024)
